<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l4"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒü vache / vnd des <expan>Chuncʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Kalben <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>ers</ex></expan> / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l5">wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brıf wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / . vnd mainen / die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / daʒ die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l6">des wol indechtig ſein / daʒ es geteydingt ſeÿ in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> maſſe als wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l7"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vormals <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Doch ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l8">das <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> beſtellet / daʒ es 
<del rend="strikethrough"> aufgeſch </del> beſteen ſol / hie <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
