<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l10"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>p<ex>ur</ex>ıfıc<ex>ationem</ex></expan> Marie / . </ab>
