<ab><expan>B<ex>ur</ex>ggrefin</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad
                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des
                <expan>Czolln<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> czü Vache und des <expan>Chuncze<ex>n</ex></expan> Kalben,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>ers</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wir
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brif wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und
            mainen die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> des wol
            indechtig sein, daz es geteydingt sey in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> masse, als wir
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vormals <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Doch so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir das
                <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> bestellet, daz es besteen sol hie
                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und des <app>
<note><q type="date">samstags cze <expan>mitvaste<ex>n</ex></expan> nu
                schirst</q>08.03.1410</note>
</app>. Wan wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>p<ex>ur</ex>ific<ex>ationem</ex></expan> Marie. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
